{"tid":1209915,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位駕駛人士注意","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:20:53.000Z","uid":234455,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46bfd9fb2e084e59274734e6ef2b56d367b71ee7","tid":1209915,"uid":234455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見於近日多宗交通事故<br />\n請多加注意車輛保養尤其是<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">使用廉價二手車</span>人士<br />\n一旦發生事故如正<span style=\"color: red;\">行經主要幹道及隧道</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在上班時段將嚴重影響交通</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 油耗：注意車輛油耗，油表顯示是否正確，<span style=\"color: red;\">避免中途死火</span><br />\n2. 輪胎：不要使用已磨損輪胎，<span style=\"color: red;\">避免因路面雜物如鐵釘刺穿輪胎</span><br />\n3. 引擎：做好清潔保養，天氣酷熱近日已<span style=\"color: red;\">發生多宗起火事故</span><br />\n<br />\n請<span style=\"color: red;\">各位車主通力合作</span>建設美好香港！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681d76a5468b0e65b5465b05c340e2551f07fa72","tid":1209915,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:42:20.000Z","msg":"仲死火?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據「道路交通條例」，在本港駕駛人士若駕車撞倒牛、豬、馬、驢、騾、山羊及綿羊等七種動物，都要停車報警，警方亦會列作交通意外處理。不過，駕駛人士如隱瞞意外便可被檢控，最高刑罰是入獄十二個月及罰款一萬元。 <br />\n該法例下，「動物」的定義並不包括貓、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>狗</strong></span>。 <br />\n對於同動物不同命，法律界人士黃國桐律師稱，估計因為該七類受保障的動物都是農民牲畜，若遇車禍死亡會造成經濟損失。"},{"pid":"db6cf584d228720b76f60124ffb6a11330c2aa83","tid":1209915,"uid":234455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"bf2d4db8ee5a062b8cc8b502786daa8470a32851","tid":1209915,"uid":167692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:50:40.000Z","msg":"我要GTR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5964d1ccc517c950233cec53d55dfee1ce1ec1a6","tid":1209915,"uid":234455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58820eb8c0b886d28be5713fb106f74befba9052","tid":1209915,"uid":234455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"681d76a5468b0e65b5465b05c340e2551f07fa72","tid":1209915,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:42:20.000Z","msg":"仲死火?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據「道路交通條例」，在本港駕駛人士若駕車撞倒牛、豬、馬、驢、騾、山羊及綿羊等七種動物，都要停車報警，警方亦會列作交通意外處理。不過，駕駛人士如隱瞞意外便可被檢控，最高刑罰是入獄十二個月及罰款一萬元。 <br />\n該法例下，「動物」的定義並不包括貓、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>狗</strong></span>。 <br />\n對於同動物不同命，法律界人士黃國桐律師稱，估計因為該七類受保障的動物都是農民牲畜，若遇車禍死亡會造成經濟損失。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"我想喺到傾實際可行方案，大家要務實團結！！！"},{"pid":"f7d51b322f5b24889d4af0e458c86af1746ce0b9","tid":1209915,"uid":234455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"推！！！"}]}